sentence: Looking at units outstanding versus one week prior within the universe of ETFs covered at ETF Channel, the biggest outflow was seen in the Consumer Discretionary Select Sector SPDR Fund ( XLY ), where 3,000,000 units were destroyed, or a 2.3% decrease week over week.
Among the largest underlying components of XLY, in morning trading today Amazon.com ( AMZN ) is up about 1.7%, and Home Depot ( HD ) is lower by about 1.4%.

And on a percentage change basis, the ETF with the biggest outflow was the WisdomTree Global ex-Mexico Equity Fund ( XMX ), which lost 600,000 of its units, representing a 16.7% decline in outstanding units compared to the week prior.
Among the largest underlying components of XMX, in morning trading today Apple ( AAPL ) is up about 2.7%, and Microsoft Corporation (MSFT) is up by about 0.5%.
